sentences: He remained active as a composer up until his sudden death of a heart attack in 2001.

Born in Toronto, Barnes entered The Royal Conservatory of Music (RCM) in 1952 where he was a pupil of Samuel Dolin (piano), Victor Feldbrill (conducting), Ernst Krenek (composition), Boyd Neel (conducting), Walter Susskind (conducting), and John Weinzweig (composition).
He graduated from the RCM in 1955 after which he entered the Vienna Academy of Music where he earned a master's degree in 1961.
